+We describe \textbf{bn-en-translate}, a fully offline Bengali-to-English neural
+machine translation system for consumer-grade GPU hardware.
+NLLB-200-distilled-600M~\cite{nllb2022} runs via CTranslate2~\cite{ctranslate2_klein}
+float16 on a single NVIDIA RTX~5050 Laptop GPU (Blackwell sm\_120, 8\,GB
+GDDR7)~\cite{nvidia_blackwell}, reaching \textbf{65.2 BLEU} on a 90-sentence
+in-domain corpus across 10 domains (4.7 News to 80.6 Health) at
