+BLEU on the 984-pair open-domain test set (sacreBLEU, no SentencePiece normalization).
+A real-time resource monitor records per-run CPU, RAM, GPU, and disk metrics to
+SQLite with automated regression detection.
+Six hardware-specific deployment constraints on first-generation Blackwell hardware
+are documented and resolved, including a cuBLAS INT8 incompatibility, a
+concurrent-pip-install SIGBUS, a fast-tokenizer fork-deadlock, a
+\texttt{prefetch\_factor} misconfiguration, an fp16/bf16 GradScaler conflict,
+and a CTranslate2 batch OOM.
+All 186 tests pass under strict TDD discipline.
